The '''Nyakuron Cultural Centre''' (or '''NCC''') ni ikigo cya leta gifite kandi kigenzurwa gishinzwe kubungabunga,  guteza imbere sinema n’umuco muri Sudani yepfo .  

== Amateka ==
Centre ya Nyakuron yubatswe nyuma y’amasezerano ya Addis Abeba yo mu 1972, arangiza intambara ya mbere ya Sudani . Iki kigo cyafunguwe ku mugaragaro mu 1976 kiyobowe na Abel Alier .  

Uruganda runini rwarimo ubusitani bunini, ikibuga cyo hanze, inzu yimyidagaduro, club nijoro hamwe na kazino. Benshi mu minsi mikuru yumuco yaho ndetse n’amahanga ikorerwa muri santere, irimo; Iserukiramuco ryamahoro rya Hagana, Iserukiramuco rya Filime rya Juba, igitaramo cya Kilkilu Ana, amarushanwa mpuzamahanga ya bokisi ndetse n’imurikagurisha. Uretse ibyo, iranakodeshwa mubikorwa byihariye nk'ubukwe. 
